1
00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:01,840
What are you doing sleeping here?

2
00:00:03,480 --> 00:00:04,880
Morning.

3
00:00:04,880 --> 00:00:06,400
Did you sleep well?

4
00:00:06,400 --> 00:00:08,680
This isn't your room, you know.

5
00:00:08,680 --> 00:00:10,440
Do you even have a clue what's going on?

6
00:00:13,920 --> 00:00:15,120
When is your birthday?

7
00:00:15,120 --> 00:00:15,640
Huh?

8
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:17,000
Your birthday.

9
00:00:18,720 --> 00:00:20,000
August 4th.

10
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:21,800
Mine is in May.

11
00:00:21,800 --> 00:00:23,040
So that makes me the older brother.

12
00:00:23,680 --> 00:00:25,280
Shut up.

13
00:00:25,280 --> 00:00:26,560
Enough talk. Get out of here.

14
00:00:29,240 --> 00:00:31,280
What's gotten into him all of a sudden?

15
00:00:32,280 --> 00:00:33,920
So gross.

16
00:00:35,640 --> 00:00:38,640
Give me a kiss before you go.

17
00:00:42,560 --> 00:00:44,240
I'm heading out.

18
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:48,840
Seeing Mom like that...

19
00:00:48,840 --> 00:00:50,160
It's just too much.

20
00:00:51,720 --> 00:00:54,080
You should try

21
00:00:54,080 --> 00:00:55,380
getting into a relationship yourself.

22
00:00:57,920 --> 00:00:59,120
Don't leave me behind.

23
00:00:59,120 --> 00:01:00,600
We live together, after all.

24
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:04,440
Don't go telling everyone

25
00:01:04,440 --> 00:01:05,440
that we live together.

26
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:07,720
Why not?

27
00:01:07,720 --> 00:01:08,720
Huh? No reason.

28
00:01:13,520 --> 00:01:15,800
Is it embarrassing to live with your brother?

29
00:01:15,800 --> 00:01:16,880
What are you talking about?

30
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:22,520
You're so cute.

31
00:01:23,320 --> 00:01:25,040
Don't touch me. You're disgusting.

32
00:01:30,240 --> 00:01:31,800
Hey, Iijima Hinata.

33
00:01:32,440 --> 00:01:33,760
Are you and Kono Mizuki close?

34
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:36,720
I guess... not really.

35
00:01:38,720 --> 00:01:41,360
Anyway, what's up with that guy?

36
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,560
Huh?

37
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:43,800
Oh.

38
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:45,560
Mizuki and I went to the same middle school.

39
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:47,520
He used to be so outgoing back then.

40
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:50,560
But once we hit high school, he just stopped talking to everyone.

41
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:55,520
Alright, let's go!
